node.text:
The world of snowboarding opens up when you find your crew. The friends you can depend on to pick you up at 4 AM on a powder day, or reminisce with after the snow melts. The companionship we find just bantering on the lift can change lives. Run after run, trip after trip, deep bonds form. They become our people.
 
You'd still get out and ride without your buddies, but with them, snowboarding becomes something bigger. Tricks and great runs are rad, but the friendships and memories we create together are timeless. Let's hear some stories ⬇️
 
🏂: @temple._.robertson & @senditwyatt
📷: @jeffurbahn
 
#WeRideTogether
